Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Panoramic views of the Brisbane CBD

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
The Aviary Toowong is the inner suburb's most anticipated and first major mixed-use precinct development for over three decades, creating a new public town square in this highly desirable location.

- A-Grade office accommodation
- Up to 21,666sqm available (average floorplate is 1,641sqm)
- Expansive views to all office levels 
- Abundance of onsite car parking
- Pristine End of Trip facilities with over 400 bicycle racks, 250 lockers and showers
- Wellness hub with large recreation deck, gym facility, pilates, yoga, massage, hair and beauty
- Rooftop restaurant and bar will provide uninterrupted views whilst entertaining clients and staff
- Located in the heart of established Toowong retail and commercial hub
- Easy public and private transport options
- Onsite Porte Cochere offering ease of access, drop off, pick up and deliveries
- Concierge Service providing easy and convenient access to a range of everyday services 
- 24/7 onsite security for the precinct and office tower, plus CCTV monitoring
- 5.5-star NABERS Energy Rating targeted

For more information, contact the exclusive agents.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: THE WORKPLACE OF THE FUTURE - DELIVERING CUSTOM-DESIGNED AND FLEXIBLE WORKSPACE SOLUTIONS

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE are pleased to offer 630 Coronation Drive for lease, a freestanding building within the popular, inner western suburb of Toowong. 

With areas ranging from 238sqm to 568sqm, the building is being offered at a competitive rent.

The existing fit out includes a boardroom, meeting room, multiple offices and large open plan area on each floor. The space offers an abundance of natural light, toilets, shower and kitchenette on each level and 12 secure carparks available. 

The building offers outstanding exposure and prominent signage to busy Coronation Drive. 

This rare whole building opportunity is centrally located within the Toowong precinct, directly opposite Toowong Village which provides staff with an abundance of retail amenity 

The property is extremely well serviced by all forms of public transport. Toowong Train Station is located across the road from the property which provides direct passage further west or back into the CBD within minutes. Toowong’s CityCat terminal is only a short walk as well as a number of major bus stops featured along Coronation Drive.

For further information or to arrange an inspection, please contact the Exclusive CBRE leasing agents.

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Central location next to Toowong Village

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
555 Coronation Drive Office Park is a modern A-Grade building in the very popular, inner western suburb of Toowong. Brand new fitouts are now completed offering tenants the opportunity to walk straight in and start business. Only one suite remaining:

Bowie Suite – 228 sqm
• Suitable for 22 staff

These tenancies are also complimented with one of the best car parking ratios in the inner city with up to 55 car bays available with the tenancy at prevailing market rates.

Toowong’s popularity stems from both its proximity to the Brisbane CBD some 4km away, but also as a major commercial and retail precinct that services the inner west. 555 Coronation Drive is located within an easy stroll to Toowong Village and provides staff with an abundance of amenity at their fingertips.

The property is extremely well serviced by all forms of public transport. Directly opposite the asset is Toowong’s CityCat terminal as well as a number of major bus stops featured along Coronation Drive. Toowong Train Station is a short 200m walk away and provides direct passage further west or back into the CBD within minutes.

Contact the listed agents to discuss your requirement today.
